Data collection began in 1933, but it presented here from 1944 onwards. The data were initially collected by the Freshwater Biological Association (FBA), then by CEH and its predecessor Institute of Freshwater Ecology (IFE) from 1989 to 2003, and subsequently again by FBA.</dcterms:description>     <dcterms:issued rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2013-09-09T14:31:03Z</dcterms:issued>     <dcterms:creator>clamw</dcterms:creator>     <dcterms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2014-02-04T11:46:25Z</dcterms:modified>     <documentcontainer:fileIdentifier xml:lang="en">9520664c-eb4d-4700-b064-5d215d23e595</documentcontainer:fileIdentifier>     <documentcontainer:catalogLink>http://data.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/9520664c-eb4d-4700-b064-5d215d23e595</documentcontainer:catalogLink>     <documentcontainer:id xml:lang="en">9520664c-eb4d-4700-b064-5d215d23e595</documentcontainer:id>     <dcterms:subject>Windermere</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Environmental monitoring facilities</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>lake</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>NERC_DDC</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>CEH Water Programme</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:title xml:lang="en">Windermere lake temperature data 1944-2002</dcterms:title>     <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2013-09-02T09:13:01Z</dcterms:created>     <dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata"/>   </documentcontainer:documentContainer> </rdf:RDF>
